metadata.name: Roadmap to E-Den I
metadata.description:
I came here with this fragment of hope, to someday be able to rebuild a small Eden of my own. A place where trees will grow, birds will sing... And finally peace and freedom will not be theories discussed, but simply an observation.

Physical drawing of 27x27cm with golden, silver, black and bronze pens on black paper ; then digitally edited to a 2777x2777 px piece. 2 versions possible, ask for your prefered one on collection!
